<p>
<note n="0104003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0104003">令＝今【明】</note>
<note n="0104004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0104004">苦＝若【明】</note>
<note n="0104005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0104005">止＝北【元】</note>
<note n="0105001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105001">偈說＝說偈【三】，【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0105002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105002">若＝名【元】</note>
<note n="0105003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105003">先＝無【三】</note>
<note n="0105004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105004">以＝言【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0105005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105005">說＝設【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0105006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105006">邏＝羅【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0106001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106001">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0106002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106002">〔汝〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0107001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107001">我＝後【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0107002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107002">唐＝此【明】</note>
<note n="0107003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107003">相＝想【元】</note>
<note n="0108001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0108001">見＝是【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0108002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0108002">密＝蜜【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109001">若＝苦【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0109002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109002">撈＝澇【宮】</note>
<note n="0109003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109003">〔般若燈論〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0109004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109004">搆＝<g ref="#CB00014">𤛓</g>【明】</note>
<note n="0109005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109005">〔現在〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110001">時＝師【宮】</note>
<note n="0110002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110002">呼＋（<g ref="#CB00069">㗚</g>）【三】</note>
<note n="0110003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110003">晝＝盡【宮】</note>
<note n="0110004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110004">〔<g ref="#CB00069">㗚</g>〕－【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0110005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110005">下＝不【明】</note>
<note n="0110006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110006">〔鞞〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110007">汝＝法【宋】【元】</note>
</p>
